<DIV>Dear all, Just wanted to warn people of kundalini syndrome =
based on my recent experience of a patient of mine. I am doing a psychiatry=
 job at present, and have been involved in the care of someone who seems to=
 think she has had a spontaneous awakening of their kundalini since childho=
od. This has involved out-of-body experiences and surges of energy in the b=
ody. She is not of Indian origin and had never heard of kundalini until her=
 symptoms started and she searched for an explanation. We have not been abl=
e to find anything physically wrong with her (all tests normal)- so it migh=
t be that this is due to deranged kundalini. Many people we call mentally i=
ll describe themselves as having a spiritual crisis, or unwanted spontaneou=
s kundalini awakening- this has triggered interest and research into this t=
opic in mainstream psychiatry. Unfortunately these patients are not well-un=
derstood by western medicine, and as we have no treatments for deranged
 ku=
ndalini, we struggle to help them. Many yogis try to forcibly waken the kun=
dalini. My experience with this lady confirmed my feeling that kundalini sh=
ould not be forcibly wakened. This woman wants to kill herself at times bec=
ause the suffering from the deranged energy is so bad. She feels it will co=
nsume her, and it is something she cannot escape from. I wondered what solu=
tion there could be to her problem. The logical one was to pray to the Divi=
ne Mother, who manifests as the kundalini to relieve the suffering of this =
woman- and either cure her, or give her the strength to bear this. May I re=
quest that the good samaritans among you pray for her, and for others like =
her (whom we may not know of)- their suffering really is pitiable. And let =
us be careful in our sadhana so as not to end up in this situation ourselve=
s. Perhaps this is why the bhakti marga is the safest. It is perhaps safest=
 to say "let me be your instrument" and leave the kundalini
 rising bit to =
God's will. Om Dum Durgayai Namaha Aparna </DIV></DIV></DIV></DIV></DIV></D=
